<ul>
  <li>1 cup flour</li>
  <li>1 cup milk</li>
  <li>1 egg</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="method">Method</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Sift the flour into a bowl.</li>
  <li>Add the milk and egg and whisk until there are no lumps.</li>
  <li>It should be quite thin - if it isnâ€™t, add more milk.</li>
  <li>Refrigerate for as long as you have patience.</li>
  <li>Heat a pan, drop in some butter and fry!</li>
</ul>
